review_blob: Wow really good smooth dark brown ale. Dark like stout or Porter but light and smooth like a lager but an ale. Definitely my favorite draft at dogfishhead brew! My first recommendation here. Try it and you wont be disappointed!

Its has a 15-18% alcohol content so its strong and robust flavor, but for what it is, the taste is pleasing. I like it much more than magic hat. Even as it looses carbonation it tastes lighter. Maybe its just me feeling better... If you are a beer explorer you have to try this on draft if you get the chance. :
